{"tid":2185492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"流浮山下白泥村約十人疑吸入不明氣體不適　消息：黑警曾通知村長會有TG訓練","createTime":"2020-09-02T09:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T13:28:34.000Z","uid":14918,"like":164,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3a4462340fe31f5d436da8790bac011dbb5095","tid":2185492,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvR73m3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvR73m3.png&h=7ff23282&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2a8f004f05353957ffb69093fafe90ca7e71715","tid":2185492,"uid":18012,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"鎮壓流浮山刀手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da78cac9fd05457825e303d97aebeccd17fdbaa9","tid":2185492,"uid":14918,"like":93,"dislike":3,"score":90,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:59:45.000Z","msg":"天水圍流浮山發生不明氣體侵襲事件，初步最少10多人感不適。下午4時許，消防人員接報流浮山下白泥近鴨仔坑士多，多人報稱聞到不明氣體感到不適，多輛救護車到場處理。<br />\n<br />\n今年6月1日流浮山亦曾疑受不明氣體侵襲，傳出氣體刺鼻、刺眼、灼痛皮膚，多人感到不適，路經現場的踏單車人士紛紛到士多買水或衝入公廁沖洗。警方其後承認，警察機動部隊當日於青山靶場進行恆常訓練，期間因風向影響，以致「訓練煙」飄向上白泥及下白泥一帶，警方當時指使用彈藥裝備均為恆常訓練所用。<br />\n<br />\n上次毒害屯門居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次連下白泥刀手都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd0ac88f202a8d9358f6091994052863ba6e87a","tid":2185492,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T10:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmo